Q_DESC:
Write a program to find the maximum of two numbers of type integer and float using function overloading.
Input:
First line contains two integers.
Second line contains two float values.
TESTCASE_1:
1 2
3.4 5.6
###---###SEPERATOR---###---
The minimum of the integer variable is 1
The minimum of the float variable is 3.4
TESTCASE_2:
0 8
6.3 10.4
###---###SEPERATOR---###---
The minimum of the integer variable is 0
The minimum of the float variable is 6.3
TESTCASE_3:
-1 -2
-10 -8
###---###SEPERATOR---###---
The minimum of the integer variable is -2
The minimum of the float variable is -10
